{"tid":934480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網友大鑊】南華早報：呂麗瑤考慮對網上攻擊採取法律行動","createTime":"2018-12-09T10:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T13:49:53.000Z","uid":202698,"like":377,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":150,"replies":[{"pid":"40a2d67558bc1cc5053c761879ad3a726ee3f1cc","tid":934480,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png&d=L0gTgPpAanD%2BxGzSQ8cmxNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=53e5c96f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png&h=5035176d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lui-11_TJlf0_1200x0.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n香港田徑代表隊「欄后」呂麗瑤去年報稱被前中學教練性侵，事後她一度遭網友質疑為何不報警，甚至對她作出種種攻擊。《<span style=\"color: red;\">南華早報》報道，呂麗瑤今日表示，正考慮對一連串攻擊她的網上言論採取法律行動。 </span><br />\n<br />\n報道指，呂麗瑤今日獲香港業餘田徑總會頒予53,000元，表揚她雅加達亞運中的表演。她在受訪時談及性侵事件，形容自己情緒已經恢復過來，「但仍有一些人繼續通過互聯網攻擊我」。 <br />\n<br />\n她指難以解釋這些網民的行為，「也許除了這種毫無意義的行為，<span style=\"color: red;\">他們無所事事。有些人甚至使用虛假的帳戶，聲稱要促進香港體育運動發局，向我索取資金。」她表示正與經理人商討，「法律行動是其中一個選項」。 </span><br />\n<br />\n呂麗瑤在去年11月30日凌晨在FB撰文，公開自已十四、五歲時被前任教練性侵的經歷，並指自己的剖白是為了喚起公眾對兒童性侵犯的關注。此一事件迅速成為全港焦點，在一開始體壇、官員、議員等一面倒表態支持呂麗瑤的勇敢行為後，網絡上亦出現不少言論，質疑呂麗瑤為何十年後才說出經歷，又批評她婉拒報警的做法，認為是對被指控者不公。 <br />\n<br />\n而在今年11月，一名曾任田徑教練的77歲退休人士黃恆，涉於8年前在大埔住所藉詞替女學員按摩，強扯對方內褲非禮，案件經審訊後裁定被告罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"0f064e00940bee7d9e1e10ff0c6a7f53dfd945e6","tid":934480,"uid":196712,"like":404,"dislike":1,"score":403,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07a0ff47b65467aae93f470cab23aabe5f651d5d","tid":934480,"uid":22675,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"有無人去過麗瑤？？我朋友想去但唔識去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/910008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/910008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c12da3f6b58e48dcf66b06988fe3c76312ad3b46","tid":934480,"uid":17103,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"嘩! 大鑊啦!"},{"pid":"839fc18901282c34b36a065e6cc4527f7845383d","tid":934480,"uid":127611,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"告非禮定強姦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e58816967dc8f0aeea7719fa1aa70cff67317a6","tid":934480,"uid":102096,"like":215,"dislike":2,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f32913980319bce33e3fb769c919780832f62217","tid":934480,"uid":79410,"like":250,"dislike":1,"score":249,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆真係好煩膠. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed98698c80f99f042713984240a7418c931b769","tid":934480,"uid":17646,"like":156,"dislike":1,"score":155,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"有經理人咁撚把撚弊"},{"pid":"f5a44fe4d425f4a52421fa3610249f97aed4ae50","tid":934480,"uid":54264,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"走數正仆街死八婆"},{"pid":"06176759d8329fe79733fc33fbc5239633498acf","tid":934480,"uid":49258,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"9e58816967dc8f0aeea7719fa1aa70cff67317a6","tid":934480,"uid":102096,"like":215,"dislike":2,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"timing 拿捏幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7613c9032d6fae05578f04416867874509750a5","tid":934480,"uid":40932,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"07a0ff47b65467aae93f470cab23aabe5f651d5d","tid":934480,"uid":22675,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"有無人去過麗瑤？？我朋